{"tid":1681141,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★用戶反映更新iOS 13.2後HomePod變磚，官方：建議用戶不要更新！！！","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T11:27:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1c2236ff6206258c608cd9f0207cd730bbac29","tid":1681141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"用戶手機更新到iOS 13.2後，新的&zwnj;13.2 HomePod&zwnj;軟件將自動安裝在&zwnj;HomePod&zwnj;上，但也可以按照HomePod軟件中的說明進行操作，以手動更新和檢查軟件版本。<br />\n<br />\nMacRumors論壇和Reddit上的多位用戶表示，該13.2更新使他們的HomePod&ldquo;變磚&rdquo;了，導致其無法使用。有遇到問題的用戶稱自己的兩個HomePod屏幕上都顯示&ldquo;白色漩渦&rdquo;，或者無限重啟，進行重置也不行，因為長按頂部按鍵不起作用。<br />\n<br />\n有些用戶在安裝新軟件後就立即出現了問題，而也有些用戶在更新後重置其設備時出現了問題。一些用戶還報告說，在更新到iOS 13.2之前安裝13.2軟件時發生了問題。<br />\n<br />\n有受影響的HomePods用戶已經聯繫了Apple支持，蘋果工作人員已經為其安排進行維修。<br />\n<br />\n目前蘋果官方還未正式回應此事，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因此建議用戶最好先不要安裝新的軟件</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/453/107.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F453%2F107.htm&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=bdd07c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/453/107.htm</a>"},{"pid":"22975dbb1a50b968df837b97bcb567d431a81815","tid":1681141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24095cd55cc82db281bf638934a6c2500722b79b","tid":1681141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08